            </div>
            <div class="mb-3">
                <div class="field-wrapper" id="freelancerNameWrapper">
                    <label for="freelancerName" class="form-label">Freelancer Name:</label>
                    <input type="text" id="freelancerName" name="freelancerName" class="form-control" disabled>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="mb-3">
                <div class="field-wrapper" id="additionalReasonWrapper">
                    <label for="additionalReason" class="form-label">Additional Reason / Rescheduled Date:</label>
                    <input type="text" id="additionalReason" name="additionalReason" class="form-control" disabled>
                    <small>*For Customer Declined/Refused Delivery, fill in the reason why the customer declined. (FMX
                        only)</small><br>
                    <small>**For Reschedule Delivery or Reschedule to Self Pick up, fill in the date of
                        reschedule. (FMX only)</small><br>
                    <small>***For Cancelled Delivery, fill in the reason why the delivery is cancelled. (All except
                        FMX)</small><br>
                    <small>****For FMX Cancelled Delivery, fill in the reason "Customer cancel order" (required) with
                        the reason (optional) why the delivery is cancelled. (FMX only)</small>
                </div>
            </div>
            <button type="submit" id="submitButton" class="btn btn-primary">Submit</button>
